76561198022040741,Recommended,312360,26169928,"Posted: 22 October, 2016",all,carretta,"This game provides a very deep simulation of the Great War. It exploits the solid AGEOD engine to reproduce all the military aspects of the period. In addition, the diplomacy is covered with a simplified but effective method. The learning curve is rather steep, but very rewarding. The game uses the WEGO system: all the sides issue orders for the following turn (two weeks), then orders of the different factions are all executed realistically at the same time. The time needed to the pc to process turns is one-two minutes, one of the shortest in AGEOD games. In conclusion, I strongly recommend this game."
